We'll meet you in 10 minutes.

559
01:10:40,152 --> 01:10:43,628
好的
All right.

560
01:10:43,629 --> 01:10:44,517
谢谢你
Thank you.

561
01:10:44,518 --> 01:10:47,980
在被发觉之前 我们可以骑马溜出去
And we can ride on out afore anyone's wiser

562
01:10:49,140 --> 01:10:50,193
