"And they shall be as one flesh."

654
01:21:36,181 --> 01:21:39,090
创世记 第二章第24节
Genesis chapter two, 24th verse.

655
01:21:39,091 --> 01:21:42,180
杰比迪亚·麦卡利斯特 你的罪已经发现了你
Your sins have found you out, Jebediah McAllister,

656
