慢慢来
Make it slow.

680
01:23:20,366 --> 01:23:22,789
杰比
Jeb! 

681
01:23:25,046 --> 01:23:28,705
你发个誓 "你不会伤害她 你会让她走"
You swear, you won't hurt her. You'll let her go.

682
01:23:28,706 --> 01:23:30,745
